Package: regressionEffects
Type: Package
Title: General Utilities for Regression Analysis 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Weber", "Christopher Robert", email = "chrisweber@arizona.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A collection of utility functions to analyze regression models. The package includes simulation features, such as bootstrapping and sampling, as well as various marginal effects estimators. The package also includes diagnostic tools, and graphing features.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
